        Capture demographics, conditions, and quick notes. View or update
        history in one place.
      </p>
      <footer class="mt1">
        <a href="/patients" role="button" class="secondary">Open Patients</a>
      </footer>
    </article>
    <article class="panel feature">
      <h3 class="m0">Doctor directory</h3>
      <p class="m0">
        Maintain the full medical staff roster by specialty so scheduling stays
        accurate.
      </p>
      <footer class="mt1">
        <a href="/doctors" role="button" class="secondary">Open Doctors</a>
      </footer>
    </article>
    <article class="panel feature">
      <h3 class="m0">Appointments</h3>
      <p class="m0">
